      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Coordination Cost Will Kill You Before Execution Speed Saves You</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Everyone optimizes for execution speed. Faster tools, better talent, tighter sprints. But the thing that actually kills teams is coordination cost. You can have the fastest team in the world and still lose if alignment eats 60% of their time.</p>
